{"tid":2050720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(64集會=機場春袋) 支聯會李卓人：我地唔需要警察出現，無警察的地方最安全","createTime":"2020-06-04T09:52:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T10:08:01.000Z","uid":84147,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0db3244be3b9720a36f7de678af08bc5682ec415","tid":2050720,"uid":84147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:52:05.000Z","msg":"世界變頭先蘋果直播，連李卓人都屌7黑警<br />\n<br />\n對老一輩藍絲黎講<br />\n唔比64集會猶如殺人父母<br />\n<br />\n今日無事 = 證明無黑警最安全，美國示威依個時勢大搞64集會，將老解黑警connect埋美國警暴，雙頭條雙重connect，同人講因為64先唔想回歸<br />\n<br />\n今日有大獲野發生 = 連64都唔比出深藍都當和理非比人拉，激嬲埋深藍中立，到時一定仲多人反警暴，仲多人反對回歸<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今晚全世界都要出呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"a66be9e219bec00485876d90405a0814d8cf959e","tid":2050720,"uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:54:14.000Z","msg":"不嬲都無黑警最安全"},{"pid":"3007258e4cb5669b3fbede005e8c06f5ae48ca98","tid":2050720,"uid":84147,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:54:54.000Z","msg":"頭先李卓人嬲到扑街<br />\n<br />\n今日黑警搞事，一定connect埋班深藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9e96fcc1e3f312b5d53e78ee013ca3b0b08249","tid":2050720,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:55:41.000Z","msg":"李卓仁屌popo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e47d98306a04f12e4d4772e8d34c7c1bd7a465d","tid":2050720,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:55:46.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">[港獨強心針]</div><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">香港最強力盟友USA : <br />\n國際反共 形勢大好<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2041520\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2041520</a></span></span></div>"},{"pid":"c15742caf4771180a31ee532f6085c4369a6992b","tid":2050720,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0